        "name": "Title",
        "value": "Evolving Concepts Regarding Radiation Therapy for Pancreatic Cancer."
      },
      {
        "name": "Abstract",
        "value": "In todays practice most institutions individualize the use of adjuvant, neoadjuvant, and definitive RT based on their interpretation of the available data. This review highlights novel concepts and approaches to the use of RT that should be considered by the surgical oncologist."
      }
